China constantly adjusts and reforms its policies. Rural revitalization is rejuvenating the nation through science and technology. Guidelines in social insurance, employment and the digital economy, among many others sectors, subtly impact the lives of everyday people. Which policies have received the most attention? Which are uniquely suited to China? Fernando Mu√±oz Bernal, a Colombian entrepreneur and vlogger who came to China in 2000, and Brian Linden, the American founder of the Linden Centre who has lived in China off and on since 1984, shared their perspectives on China's policy evolution.